		<div class="act-heading" style="background:#f62217">Past Activities</div>
			<div class="act-subheading" style="background:#842dce; "> Drinking Water</div>
			<div class="act-defi">Sansthan has made 126 public water tanks and 60 small water tanks in between 1995 to 2008 to help week and poor families with the help of Jan vikas Ahmadabad, Action and International India New DELHI , CAPART Jaipur. This programm has benifited approximately 3870 families of 30 villages.
								  So now the people of villages dont have to go miles to fetch drinkig water. Instead they now harvest rain water that is then used the whole year.</div>
			
			<div class="act-subheading" style="background:#463e41; "> Human Resource Development</div>
			<div class="act-defi">For the development of human resource in 60 villages gram level committees and 15 gram panchayat committees were formed by gramin vikas sansthanwhich look after the developments in their area.
								People now learn how to work in a team and also solve each others and villagers problems on their level. Otherwise they reach higher authorities for a solution.
</div>
			
			
			<div class="act-subheading" style="background:#52d017; "> Panchayati Raj Kanoon</div>
			<div class="act-defi">Helped in starting work under panchayati raj in 10 gram panchayats where members of gram sabha, ward panch and sarpanch are informed about the power and rights of panchayat which are provided under rajasthan Panchyati Raj Adhinium 1994 . We also work hard to remove some society problems of castism, child marriage, dowry, etc.</div>
			
			<div class="act-subheading" style="background:#fdd017; "> Lok Adhikar Pariyojana</div>
			<div class="act-defi">Lokadhikar Pariyojan currently running since 2001 in 7 villages of Dhorimmana panchayat samiti, Barmmer. Main objective of this project is to provide rights to backward classes and help villagers get their rights from government. 
			
			</div>
			
			<div class="act-subheading" style="background:#306eff; "> Aids Jan chetna program</div>
			<div class="act-defi">We imparted the basic information about AIDS, its modes of transmission and its preventions to the people in villages dhorimmana, Cohtan, sindhari in the year 2005 with the help Rajasthan State Control Society and Sawasthya Seva, Rajasthan Sarkar, Jaipur . Under the Jan Chetana programme we arranged team of six actors who imparted the information in form of plays, pupppet shows, songs , etc.</div>
			
			<div class="act-subheading" style="background:#f62217; "> Women Self Help Group</div>
			<div class="act-defi">Established women self help group in 25 villages and also provided training to these women. We organized a fare for these women in which around 1000 ladies made their presence felt.</div>
			
			<div class="act-subheading" style="background:Green; "> Health Program</div>
			<div class="act-defi">With the help of JRD TATA Trust in Dhorimana we organized the health education and primaray scheme in 20 villages. This was a huge program spread in a time span of 3 years. Under this programme we informed the villagers about basic hygiene which leads to many diseases, viral diseases and there cures. It was mainly aimedd at women and their health. Many Birth attendants were given training for safer delivery and basic procedures to be followed after the birth.
			Vaccination of children below the age of 5 was done on a huge scale . Also the pregnant womens were immunized and given necessary tablets.With the help of animators we provided treatment to 0-6 year old children .Thus thevillagers got benefits of this health programme and got aware of few health problem’s and their treatments.</div>
		
		
		
		
	
	
